title: install obfs4proxy in Whonix-Gateway 11 by default
description:
We should probably install [`obfs4proxy`](https://packages.debian.org/jessie/obfs4proxy) by default, no?

To be added as `Depends:` to [`anon-gateway-packages-recommended`](https://github.com/Whonix/anon-meta-packages/blob/f400f82ad493befede7a78356e026b297d2ec7ba/debian/control#L61).
